AB  - Doctoral dissertation examining the layered psychological impacts of torture alongside structural post-migration systemic abuse. The research utilizes quantitative clinical metrics and qualitative feedback to trace trauma symptom profiles among permanent refugee residents, community-based asylum seekers, and administrative immigration detainees across Australia.
